description: *OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED- OFFER ACCEPTED! This adorable one-bedroom condo, with a modern kitchen that features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, is ready for you. Conveniently located just one block from the West Broadway shops and restaurants and steps to the Seaport area, this well-maintained unit has an open floor plan, a comfortable living room with a gas fireplace, and sliders that lead to a private deck. Other features include a spacious bedroom with a large closet, a jacuzzi bath with ceramic tile, and a spacious storage unit with a new washer/dryer storage. There's also room in the clean common area of the basement for exercise equipment. This is a great entry-level unit!
